  "texts": [
    "The task of the decoder is to compute decisions regarding the placement of stations and the scheduling of jobs.",
    "In the layout planning task, the control algorithm must determine new coordinates for a station.",
    "The action space corresponds to all possible coordinates on the shop floor.",
    "A 128 × 128 grid discretizes the layout.",
    "Independence of the action space and the shop floor size is thus given."
  ],
